column5: So there we were just drifting around and then BAM!!!! This whale jumps on us!!!!
I thought there was a law where humans and not to go within a certain distance of Whales. I guess not. Whale vs. Kayak, my money is on the Whale.
I cant believe people starting clapping and laughing when that whale landed on those people.  Good to see no one got seriously injured.
It missed them or they would be squished.      would be neat to see close up.
Yes,I think they sink a little faster than us.So close,imagine that happening to you?,keep the float-able camera going.Thinking I may of soiled my trunks .

I thought there was a law where humans and not to go within a certain distance of Whales. I guess not. Whale vs. Kayak, my money is on the Whale.  In some countries there is. But there is no law saying that the whales have to stay away from you.
